Chinabank has completed a full transition to an AI-powered human capital management system, aiming to simplify HR and improve the employee experience for over 11,000 staff. The bank introduced this new platform, called SyncHROne, in partnership with Darwinbox. With AI at its core, the system is already changing how HR functions are managed across all branches and offices. https://www.blockchain-council.org/certifications/certified-artificial-intelligence-ai-expert/
